| comment "Dragnet [Ransomware]: dragnet-ransomware-2024-1653 — Recovery Inhibition (lockbit3)"
| comment "Status: experimental | Level: high | ID: c8ea2e92-bc85-54b4-bee9-5391ed9d1d63"
